We ve created new updates just for you. Here s what s new: React to task comments with Emojis and inject a little more fun into your working day. Discover new smarter layouts that make room for even greater productivity. 2018 is going to be a big year for DropTask. Here s what s new: New block shaped tasks are now available in the Workflow Calendar Completed Tasks and Urgency Lists view. Enjoy the satisfaction of striking through completed tasks and watch them fade away beautifully with a brand new animation. Choose to keep Completed Tasks visible on your projects for up to 7 days. Cleaner interface in Urgency Lists View previously List View for a sharper focus of your priorities. Celebrate productivity streaks with new Achievements A choice of normal high and very high urgency and importance levels on tasks across all views Tasks that were previously set as low urgency will now have a low urgency tag All round improvements and fixes to make your life a little easier and more productive.
